import React from 'react'; import Carousel from 'react-bootstrap/Carousel' import '../index.css' import Menorahsauraus_1 from '../Assets/Crafts/Menorahsauraus.jpeg' import Menorahsauraus_2 from '../Assets/Crafts/Menorahsauraus_lit.jpeg' import Window_Wide from '../Assets/Crafts/Window_Wide.jpg' import Window_Close from '../Assets/Crafts/Window_Close.jpg' import Frank_1 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_1.jpg' import Frank_2 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_2.jpg' import Frank_3 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_3.jpg' import Frank_4 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_4.jpg' import Frank_5 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_5.jpg' import Frank_6 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_6.jpg' import Frank_7 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_7.jpg' import Frank_8 from '../Assets/Crafts/Frank_8.jpg' const menorahsauraus = [Menorahsauraus_1, Menorahsauraus_2] const window = [Window_Wide, Window_Close] const frank = [Frank_1, Frank_2, Frank_3, Frank_4, Frank_5, Frank_6, Frank_7, Frank_8] const Crafts = () => { return (
{menorahsauraus.map((menorahsauraus, i) => { return })} {window.map((window, i) => { return })}
) } export default Crafts;
